===Adjective===
{{en-adj|head=[[color]] [[blind]]}}

# {{context|of a|person or animal|lang=en}} Unable to distinguish between two or more primary colors (usually red and green).
# {{context|of a|person|lang=en}} Holding no prejudice based on skin color; not paying attention to skin color.
# {{context|of a|process|lang=en}} Which does not consider [[race]].

